property.name: KINSOKU_PUSH_IN_FIRST
property.shortdesc: Attempts to move characters to the previous line; if the push-in is not possible, pushes characters to the next line.

property.name: KINSOKU_PUSH_OUT_FIRST
property.shortdesc: Attempts to move characters to the next line; if the push-out is not possible, pushes characters to the previous line.

property.name: KINSOKU_PUSH_OUT_ONLY
property.shortdesc: Always moves characters to the next line. Does not attempt a push-in.
